Package: vgplotr
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Visualizations with Mosaic and DuckDB
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("UW Interactive Data Lab", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "idl@cs.washington.edu")
    )
Description: Create interactive, database-driven visualizations using the Mosaic
    framework. Provides an R interface to vgplot, a visualization grammar inspired
    by ggplot2 and Vega-Lite, with full DuckDB integration for scalable data processing.
    Works seamlessly in Quarto documents, RMarkdown, and Shiny applications.
